?Uplift?
ïï
What does this word mean to you?
ïï
When I think of this word I canít help but think of @gabbybernstein ës quote...îYour presence is your power.î
ïï
My MO is to do ALL the things ...and do them all at once.  Itís engrained in my brain (how exhausting!)...and if I donít step back from the noise I am left exhausted, depleted, irritable (just ask my hubby!!).
ïï
Today I had the incredible opportunity to jump in live in our @zyiaactive Corporate group to talk about this word..UPLIFT...and what it meant to me.  Because these are the things that this company holds as utmost importance in our lives + this world
ïï
I got to share the fact that it is incredibly important to take time to reflect on how you want to show up each day + each moment, to pinpoint the things In Life that allow us to show up this way, and the things in life that keep us from feeling this way.
ïï
When we take time to do this, we become uplifted...and from that we uplift those around us.
ïï
Take time for YOU + do the things in life that uplift your presence ?? #upliftzyia #yourpresenceisyourpower #uplift #bethelight
